trans-unit.source: Represents a design-time editor sheet for the properties of a resource expression in the UI of a designer host at design time.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et ark utformingen redigeringsprogrammet for egenskaper av et ressursen uttrykk i Brukergrensesnittet designer vert under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor> class with the ResourceExpressionEditorSheet class to select the individual properties of a resource reference expression, and to combine the selected resource expression property values into a resource expression.
trans-unit.target: Den visuelle utformeren bruker den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor>klasse klassen ResourceExpressionEditorSheet Velg individuelle egenskaper for en referanseuttrykket for ressursen og kombinere egenskapsverdier for valgte ressurs-uttrykk i et uttrykk.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ConnectionStringsExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method returns a ResourceExpressionEditorSheet object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ConnectionStringsExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden returnerer et ResourceExpressionEditorSheet-objekt.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ConnectionStringsExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In the expressions dialog box, when you select a control property and bind it to a resource expression, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Når du velger egenskap for en kontroll og binde til et uttrykk for ressursen, kaller i dialogboksen uttrykk for den visuelle utformeren den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditor.GetExpressionEditorSheet%2A>

trans-unit.source: The visual designer uses the returned ResourceExpressionEditorSheet object to prompt for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ClassKey%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ResourceKey%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Den visuelle utformeren bruker returnerte ResourceExpressionEditorSheet-objektet til å be om den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ClassKey%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ResourceKey%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ResourceKey%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ClassKey%2A>

trans-unit.source: Once the resource expression properties are selected, the visual designer calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A> method to combine the properties into a resource expression string.
trans-unit.target: Når uttrykket ressursegenskaper er valgt, den visuelle utformeren kaller den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>metode for å kombinere egenskapene i et uttrykk ressursstrengen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.GetExpression%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ResourceKey%2A> property must be specified in a resource expression; it indexes the resource value.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ResourceKey%2A>må være angitt i et uttrykk som ressursen; indekserer Ressursverdien for.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ResourceKey%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ClassKey%2A> property is optional.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ClassKey%2A>egenskapen er valgfrie.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ClassKey%2A>

trans-unit.source: It references the class key or file name that defines the resource in the global resources folder.
trans-unit.target: Den refererer til nøkkelen, eller fil klassenavnet som definerer ressursen i mappen globale ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The initial <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ClassKey%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ResourceKey%2A> property values are set using the input `expression` string.
trans-unit.target: Første <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ClassKey%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ResourceKey%2A>egenskapsverdier angis ved hjelp av inndataene `expression` streng.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ResourceKey%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ResourceExpressionEditorSheet.ClassKey%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A> property is set using the input `serviceProvider` implementation.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>egenskapen angis ved hjelp av inndataene `serviceProvider` implementering.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ExpressionEditorSheet.ServiceProvider%2A>

trans-unit.source: A resource expression, used to initialize the expression editor sheet.
trans-unit.target: Et uttrykk, brukes til å starte uttrykket redigeringsprogrammet arket.

trans-unit.source: A service provider implementation supplied by the designer host, used to obtain additional design-time services.
trans-unit.target: En tjenesten leverandøren implementering angitt av designer verten, brukes til å hente utformingen tilleggstjenester.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the key that matches the filename for the resource in the project's global resource folder.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir nøkkel som samsvarer med filnavnet for ressursen i prosjektets global-ressurs-mappen.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], global resource files are located in the App_GlobalResources folder.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], globale ressursfiler ligger i mappen app_globalresources.

trans-unit.source: The key for a resource file in the global resource folder.
trans-unit.target: Nøkkelen for en ressursfil i mappen global-ressurs.

trans-unit.source: Returns a resource expression that is formed by the expression editor sheet property values.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et uttrykk som er utformet av egenskapsverdiene for uttrykket redigeringsprogrammet arket.

trans-unit.source: The resource expression string for the current settings in the sheet.
trans-unit.target: Uttrykket ressursstrengen for de gjeldende innstillingene i arket.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the resource expression string is valid.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om uttrykket ressursstrengen er gyldig.

trans-unit.source: This base implementation always returns `true`.
trans-unit.target: Denne base implementeringen alltid returnerer `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the resource expression string is valid; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis uttrykket ressursstrengen er gyldig. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the resource, which is used as a key to find the resource value.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på ressursen, som brukes til å finne ressurser som en nøkkel.

trans-unit.source: The ResourceKey property is required for a resource expression; it indicates the name of the resource.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ResourceKey kreves for en ressurs-uttrykk. Angir navnet på ressursen.

trans-unit.source: The name of the resource is used at both run time and design time to look up a resource and assign it to a control property.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på ressursen brukes på både Kjør og utforming til å åpne en ressurs, og tilordne den til en kontrollegenskap.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label.Text%2A> property for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> control is assigned to the resource expression `<%$ Resources:Strings, labelText $>`, the resource expression is evaluated and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label.Text%2A> field is assigned to the `labelText` resource value in the `Strings` class.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label.Text%2A>egenskapen for et <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label>kontrollen er tilordnet til ressurs-uttrykket `<%$ Resources:Strings, labelText $>`, ressurs-uttrykket evalueres og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label.Text%2A>felt er tilordnet til den `labelText` ressurs-verdi i den `Strings` klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label.Text%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Label.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the resource.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på ressursen.
